  "abstract": "The Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System (Board) is announcing that the Federal Reserve Banks (Reserve Banks) will adopt the ISO[supreg] 20022 message format for the Fedwire[supreg] Funds Service on a single day, March 10, 2025. The Board is also announcing a revised testing strategy, backout strategy, and other details concerning the implementation of the ISO 20022 message format for the Fedwire Funds Service.",
